			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-14121" title="Natural's Night Out" src="http://www.sparkplugpeople.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/Naturals-Night-Out1.jpg" alt="Naturals Night Out1 Naturals Night Out hits NYC for a 2nd Year to Celebrate Natural Hair " width="610" height="424" /></p>
<p>New York, NY (June 5th, 2012) &#8211; Chicandkinky.com created Natural&#8217;s Night Out to help women of all shades reinvent the love for natural hair. Hundreds of women will convene at Natural&#8217;s Night Out (NNO) taking place on Sunday June 10th, 2012 at the Midtown Loft and Terrace from 12p-8p.</p>
<p>The Midtown Loft &amp; Terrace is located at 267 5th Avenue, New York, NY 10016 in the heart of the city. Join Chicandkinky.com and top industry leaders and other inspiring individuals in the natural hair community for this one-day empowering event that promises to give attendees the tools and information so they can have confidence in wearing their natural hair.</p>
<p>Natural&#8217;s Night Out attendees will gain inspiration from an astronomical line-up of some of the most influential people such as Ylorie Anderson of EDENS Body Works, Celebrity Hair Artist, Nedjetti Harvey, Curly Celebrity Stylist, Tameeka McNeil Johnson &#038; Hair Stylist Jennifer Rose, Ketlie Hyacinthe of Design Essentials, and many more.</p>
<p>&#8220;Natural&#8217;s Night Out is the perfect opportunity for women who are looking for new ways to reinvent and create styles and care for their natural hair and establish long-lasting relationships with other naturals. Natural hair will always be in, but one thing that&#8217;s always in style are memorable moments with other naturalistas,&#8221; says creator Bre Syliva.</p>
<p>Natural&#8217;s Night Out will feature:</p>
<ul>
<li>Express Manicures by Ginger + Liz</li>
<li>Mini Massages by Grae Therapy</li>
<li>Cocktails by FRAGOLI</li>
<li>Cupcakes by BcakeNY</li>
<li>Unleash Your Curls Terrace Party sponsored by Curls Unleashed</li>
</ul>
<p><span><br />
Natural&#8217;s Night Out is sponsored by: Design Essentials, Beautiful Textures, Curls Unleashed, CURLS, Curl Max, EDEN Body Works, Jane Carter Solutions</span></p>
<p>Additional Participants include: Carol&#8217;s Daughter, Blue Magic, Jessi Curl, Pooka Pure and Simple<em> and</em> more.</p>
<p>About ChicandKinky.com:<br />
<a href="http://chicandkinky.com">ChicandKinky.com</a> was created in 2009 to celebrate the increase of natural hair and beauty in women of all shades. It is a social media platform designed to merge the elevation of natural hair and a fabulous lifestyle. The choice to go natural has grown tremendously over the years and can be seen more frequently all around the world. The importance is to spread the education of healthy natural hair so that we can <em>abolish</em> the myth of “good hair,”  which is important to us. Accepting your hair for each kink, coil and curl is the ideal goal for us at Chicandkinky.com. Natural hair care should and could be very simple and Chic and Kinky is here to help. From the latest products to styles, ChicandKinky.com is the place for you to obtain all the information you need. Three friends with addictive personalities and the readiness to learn make Chicandkinky.com the successful site it is today. Follow us on Twitter @Chicandkinky</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">###</p>
<p>For more information about Natural&#8217;s Night Out or interview requests, please contact: Brenda Barthelemybrenda@luxurychicmedia.com or call 347.602.2913</p>
