		<title>Cocktails in the Garden ~  Drink in the Beauty of Atlanta’s Urban Oasis!</title>
		<link>http://www.sparkplugpeople.com/cocktails-in-the-garden-drink-in-the-beauty-of-atlanta%e2%80%99s-urban-oasis/</link>
		<comments>http://www.sparkplugpeople.com/cocktails-in-the-garden-drink-in-the-beauty-of-atlanta%e2%80%99s-urban-oasis/#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Wed, 16 May 2012 20:45:53 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator>PYNTK</dc:creator>
				<category><![CDATA[Press Releases]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Atlanta Botanical Gardens]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Atlanta Urban Beauty]]></category>
