		<title>5 Reasons Women Need to Feel Good About Their Lives Right Now!</title>
		<link>http://www.sparkplugpeople.com/5-reasons-women-need-to-feel-good-about-their-lives-right-now/</link>
		<comments>http://www.sparkplugpeople.com/5-reasons-women-need-to-feel-good-about-their-lives-right-now/#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Wed, 09 May 2012 09:00:38 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator>PYNTK</dc:creator>
				<category><![CDATA[Articles]]></category>

		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.sparkplugpeople.com/?p=12158</guid>
		<description><![CDATA[1. You have a mission to accomplish! You are not here on earth merely to exist. You have a purpose, something special to offer the world and people are waiting for you to manifest this gift and bless their lives. The importance and urgency of your dream, calling, idea or goal prompts you to take [...]]]></description>
			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-12164" title="Happiness" src="http://www.sparkplugpeople.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/Happiness.jpg" alt="Happiness 5 Reasons Women Need to Feel Good About Their Lives Right Now!" width="610" height="641" /></p>
<h2><span style="color: #993300;">1. You have a mission to accomplish!</span></h2>
<p>You are not here on earth merely to exist. You have a purpose, something special to offer the world and people are waiting for you to manifest this gift and bless their lives. The importance and urgency of your dream, calling, idea or goal prompts you to take action. Tomorrow is promised to no one, but you have your life right now. You must get your life back because you can&#8217;t quit and you can&#8217;t surrender &#8212; you are a woman on a mission!</p>
<h2><span style="color: #993300;">2. Surprise! You already have the resources you need!</span></h2>
<p>What is it that you have in your hand? What experiences have you gone through? Who have you met? What lessons have you learned? What burns in your heart? Wow! You are already qualified, trained, talented or experienced in some specific area. You have gone through so much and sacrificed too much to continue on an unfulfilling life path because of &#8220;feelings.&#8221; You probably know that time doesn&#8217;t stand still in the hope that you will be in the right mood or frame of mind to act. The longer you wait, the slimmer your chances of action become. You deserve to feel good about your present and past accomplishments and what you can still do. Stand up and be counted today!</p>
<h2><span style="color: #993300;">3. You are alive, energetic, creative, resourceful, strong, able and willing.</span></h2>
<p>There may never be another moment like this moment. The perfect time is when you are motivated, full of energy and in good health. If you can see, hear, think, read, talk, or walk &#8212;you are alive! You have every right in the world to feel good about your life! This is the time for you to churn creative and fresh ideas, turning them into reality. Get excited about something and &#8220;strike while the iron is hot!&#8221; Live your life fully now!</p>
<h2><span style="color: #993300;">4. Opportunities are everywhere &#8212; waiting to be seized by you.</span></h2>
<p>There are so many opportunities, waiting to be seized by someone who will take the risk and do what is required. That someone is you! There is no time left to bemoan your life &#8230; this is your moment. Today is the time to move to the next level. Make that phone call, start that business, sign up for that class, forgive that person, help the needy, pursue that goal, pay off that debt, invest in that venture, go on that adventure, love again &#8212; believe again! A new phase has begun. Embrace it and move forward with confidence!</p>
<h2><span style="color: #993300;">5. You can choose to do better for yourself today.</span></h2>
<p>If you choose to put in the work required, you can earn more money, eat healthy, gain respect, reduce your stress, increase your happiness, find a good relationship, stop tolerating stuff that doesn&#8217;t work and so forth. Your foremost responsibility is to yourself. Give yourself a chance to attain your goals. Make the right choices and decisions, put your best foot forward and do everything necessary to ensure that you achieve success. What are you choosing today?</p>
<p>You can feel good again &#8230; yes, it&#8217;s possible! But first, you must get motivated toward a worthwhile goal &#8230; your life!</p>
<p><a href="http://www.motivationzone.com">Caroline Jalango</a> is a life strategist and motivational coach for women who want to do better for themselves. She is the author of &#8220;Settle for Less No More&#8221; and &#8220;You Deserve to Feel Good&#8221; motivational books for women who want to succeed. For more topics like this, visit http://www.motivationzone.com to gain the momentum to do better for yourself and get the results you want!</p>
